  "title": "Accounts Assistant – Multiple Openings (Various Locations)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Salary: $2600 to $3200 + VB</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Bugis / Central / East / West (Multiple Openings)</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: Normal Working Hours</strong></li><li><strong>Accounting / Admin Duties</strong></li><li><strong>TRAINING PROVIDED</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p></p><p><u><strong>Accounting Support:</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Assist in preparing and processing invoices, payment vouchers, and receipts.</li><li>Bookkeeping tasks, including accounts payable and receivable tracking.</li><li>Help with bank and petty cash reconciliations and maintain up-to-date financial records.</li><li>Maintain accurate and organized records of financial documents for audit and reporting purposes.</li><li>Support the preparation of monthly reports and assist during audits.</li></ul><p></p><p><u><strong>Administrative Support:</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Monitor and manage office supplies, equipment, and vendor coordination.</li><li>Handle general communication such as answering phone calls and managing emails.</li><li>Maintain filing systems (both electronic and physical) for administrative and accounting documents.</li><li>Provide general assistance to the team and management for administrative or finance-related projects and tasks as needed.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience: At least 1-2 years of experience in Admin & Accounts or related roles.</li><li>Familiarity with simple accounts and finance</li></ul><p></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
